Interface IErpDB

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Customer, Item

    public interface IErpDB
    Interface used for unification of functionality. Not all ERP entities have implemented this functionality - only Customer and Product. It was created only for demo purposes, that it is possible to unify functionality on ERP objects.
